<eesti>&Uuml;leminekus&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>Transitional Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kuni 2001. aasta 1. oktoobrini antavad rahvusvahelise autoveo tegevusload ja s&otilde;idukikaardid kehtivad neil m&auml;rgitud kehtivusaja l&otilde;puni, kuid mitte kauem kui 2002. aasta 1. oktoobrini. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Activity licences and licence cards for international road transport issued until 1 October 2001 are valid until the expiry date indicated thereon, but not for longer than until 1 October 2002. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kuni 2002. aasta 1. oktoobrini on rahvusvahelisel autoveol omavahendite n&otilde;utav suurus 48 000 krooni iga kasutatava mootors&otilde;iduki kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The amount of own funds required upon international road transport is 48 000 kroons per used motor vehicle until 1 October 2002. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist antud rahvusvahelise autoveo tegevusloa aluseks olev ametialast p&auml;devust t&otilde;endav koolitustunnistus kehtib 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarini. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Certificates of training in proof of professional competence on the basis of which activity licences for international road traffic are issued prior to the entry into force of this Act are valid until 1 January 2003. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist antud autojuhi rahvusvahelise autoveo koolitustunnistus j&auml;&auml;b kehtima. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Certificates of training in international road transport issued to drivers prior to the entry into force of this Act remain valid. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 36. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 36. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse rakendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Implementation of Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esolev seadus j&otilde;ustub 2000. aasta 1. oktoobril. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) This Act enters into force on 1 October 2000. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 4 s&auml;testatud n&otilde;ue korraldada tasulist riigisisest ja rahvusvahelist autovedu tegevusloa ja s&otilde;idukikaardi alusel ning &sect; 9 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatud n&otilde;ue korraldada oma kulul rahvusvahelist autovedu tegevusloa ja s&otilde;idukikaardi alusel j&otilde;ustuvad 2001. aasta 1. oktoobril. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The requirement provided for in &sect; 4 of this Act to organise internal and international road transport for hire or reward on the basis of activity licences and licence cards and the requirement provided for in subsection 9 (2) of this Act to organise international road transport on own account on the basis of activity licences and licence cards enter into force on 1 October 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Tasulisel riigisisesel autoveol kohaldatakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 6 l&otilde;ikes 4 s&auml;testatud omavahendite suuruse n&otilde;uet alates: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The requirement provided for in subsection 6 (4) of this Act concerning the amount of own funds upon internal road transport for hire or reward appplies as of: </inglise>
<eesti>1) 2001. aasta 1. oktoobrist 30 protsendi ulatuses &sect; 6 l&otilde;ikes 4 etten&auml;htud suurusest; </eesti>
<inglise>1) 1 October 2001, to the extent of 30 per cent of the amount prescribed in subsection 6 (4); </inglise>
<eesti>2) 2002. aasta 1. oktoobrist 100 protsendi ulatuses &sect; 6 l&otilde;ikes 4 etten&auml;htud suurusest. </eesti>
<inglise>2) 1 October 2002, to the extent of 100 per cent of the amount prescribed in subsection 6 (4). </inglise>
<eesti>(4) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 6 l&otilde;ikes 4 s&auml;testatud omavahendite suuruse n&otilde;uet kohaldatakse tasulisel rahvusvahelisel autoveol alates 2002. aasta 1. oktoobrist. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The requirement prescribed in subsection 6 (4) of this Act concerning the amount of own funds applies in international road transport for hire or reward as of 1 October 2002. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 7 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud ametialase p&auml;devuse n&otilde;uet kohaldatakse tasulisel autoveol alates 2001. aasta 1. oktoobrist. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The professional competence requirement provided for in subsection 7 (1) of this Act applies in road transport for hire or reward as of 1 October 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-des 27 ja 28 s&auml;testatud alarms&otilde;idukijuhi koolituse n&otilde;uet ning &sect;-s 22 s&auml;testatud kohustust koolitustunnistuse kontrollimiseks esitamise kohta kohaldatakse t&ouml;&ouml;le v&otilde;etava alarms&otilde;idukijuhi suhtes alates 2001. aasta 1. juulist ja t&ouml;&ouml;tava alarms&otilde;idukijuhi suhtes alates 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarist. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The requirement provided for in &sect;&sect; 27 and 28 of this Act for training of drivers of emergency vehicles and the requirement provided for in &sect; 22 of this Act to produce certificates of training for inspection apply to drivers of emergency vehicles to be employed as of 1 July 2001 and to drivers of emergency vehicles already employed as of 1 January 2003. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-des 27 ja 28 s&auml;testatud riigisisese autoveo autojuhi ametikoolituse tunnistuse n&otilde;uet ning &sect;-s 22 s&auml;testatud kohustust koolitustunnistuse kontrollimiseks esitamise kohta kohaldatakse alates 2005. aasta 1. jaanuarist. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) The requirement provided for in &sect;&sect; 27 and 28 of this Act for drivers of vehicles in internal road transport to hold certificates of training and the requirement provided for in &sect; 22 of this Act to produce certificates of training for inspection apply as of 1 January 2005. </inglise>
<eesti>Alates 2002. aasta 1. juulist on vedajal keelatud v&otilde;tta t&ouml;&ouml;le t&ouml;&ouml;lepingu alusel autojuhti, kes ei ole k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 27 s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uete kohast koolitust l&auml;binud. </eesti>
<inglise>Carriers are prohibited from employing, on the basis of a contract of employment, drivers who have not passed the training provided for in &sect; 27 of this Act as of 1 July 2002. (1) RT = Riigi Teataja = State Gazette </inglise>
